liWiki\\n- Pseudomonas PA3529 from PMID:21674802 by PseudoCAP\\n\\n\\n\",\n\n  Line 10:       \"body\": \"Dear all, \\n\\nThe proposal has been made to obsolete GO:0008785 alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity.\\n\\n* The reason for obsoletion is that it is more specific than the specificity of any known gene product.\\n\\nExperimental annotations\\nEcoliWiki 1\\nPseudoCAP 1\\n\\nNo InterPro2GO/UniRule/UniProtKW mappings.\\n\\nAnnotations can be viewed here: \\nhttps://github.com/geneontology/go-annotation/issues/6396\\n\\nThis term is being replaced by GO:0102039 NADH-dependent peroxiredoxin activity\\n\\nAny comments can be  added to the issue: https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31961\\n\\n\\nThanks, \\n\",\n\n  Line 25:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please obsolete GO:0008785 alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity.\",\n\n  Line 57:   \"title\": \"obsolete GO:0008785  alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity\",\n\n\n/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__pr_result__/src/ontology/ld.txt:\n  Line 5677: intersection_of: capable_of GO:0008785 ! alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity\n\n\n/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__pr_result__/src/ontology/go-idranges.txt:\n  Line 7380: GO:0008785\tMA\talkyl hydroperoxide reductase\n\n\n/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__pr_result__/src/ontology/go-edit.obo:\n  Line 85578: id: GO:0008785\n\n  Line 92765: comment: See also the molecular function term 'alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity ; GO:0008785'.\n\n  Line 385457: comment: See also the molecular function term 'alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity ; GO:0008785'.\n\n\n/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__pr_result__/src/ontology/comments.txt:\n  Line 1386: comment: See also the molecular function term 'alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity ; GO:0008785'.\n\n  Line 3966: comment: See also the molecular function term 'alkyl hydroperoxide reductase activity ; GO:0008785'.\n\n\n/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/src/ontolo